Class IGInterpreterCode

    public class IGInterpreterCode
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Author:
    Guenter Bartsch This class holds compiled code for a process which was not synthesizable and therefore is represented by a process interpreter component in the netlist. the interpreter is a stack machine
